STATE
v.
Chaumon Marte WEBB. No. 450P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 19, 2006. Clark Everett, District Attorney, for State. Jarvis John Edgerton, IV, for Webb.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 18th day of August 2005 by Plaintiff for Temporary Stay:

"Motion for Stay Dissolved by order of the Court in conference this the 19th day of December 2006."
